WEBVTT

00:34.350 --> 00:35.310
Auntie,

00:36.790 --> 00:38.920
are you my father's new consort?

00:39.110 --> 00:42.000
You're not as pretty as
my mother or my other mother.

00:49.070 --> 00:49.960
"Auntie"?

00:50.280 --> 00:51.200
Call me Sister.

00:51.220 --> 00:53.150
And who are you calling not pretty?

00:53.200 --> 00:55.960
You have to pay for it! Pay for it!

00:56.000 --> 00:57.150
-Pay for it!
-Alright, alright.

00:57.150 --> 00:58.070
Okay, stop.

00:58.880 --> 01:00.280
I heard it the first time.

01:04.349 --> 01:05.150
Am I amazing?

01:05.420 --> 01:05.990
Amazing!

01:06.750 --> 01:07.800
You little brat.

01:09.190 --> 01:11.650
I've long heard that Lady Xie
is not interested in embroidery,

01:11.650 --> 01:12.860
cares nothing for the refined arts,

01:12.860 --> 01:13.680
neglects proper pursuits,

01:13.680 --> 01:15.080
and behaves arrogantly.

01:15.560 --> 01:16.760
But seeing you today,

01:16.760 --> 01:18.680
I find you clever and full of spirit—

01:18.680 --> 01:20.210
quite delightful, in fact.

01:23.020 --> 01:24.950
I've also heard that your marriage
was an unhappy one,

01:24.950 --> 01:26.400
that you've lived
in loneliness and resentment.

01:26.400 --> 01:27.490
Yet seeing you today,

01:27.490 --> 01:28.660
you're actually content and at ease,

01:28.660 --> 01:30.460
carefree as the breeze, Yuanji.

01:30.800 --> 01:33.330
Clearly, not every rumor
is worth believing.

01:33.530 --> 01:34.920
Mother rarely goes out

01:35.150 --> 01:36.680
because she's too poor.

01:37.000 --> 01:39.350
Every time she does,
she can't resist buying books.

01:39.350 --> 01:40.580
And they're very expensive.

01:40.580 --> 01:44.240
One ancient scroll costs as much as
three of my Nine-Linked Rings.

01:45.740 --> 01:47.200
I don't have many hobbies.

01:47.250 --> 01:48.850
I just like to collect books.

01:49.039 --> 01:50.280
Just these past few days, I even found

01:50.280 --> 01:52.300
about 20 scrolls
of interesting unofficial history

01:52.300 --> 01:55.700
and several baskets of religious scriptures
from the Western Regions.

01:55.700 --> 01:56.289
Oh,

01:56.320 --> 01:59.250
and a few books of tales
from the previous dynasty...

01:59.910 --> 02:01.070
Once I start talking about books,

02:01.070 --> 02:02.040
I tend to ramble.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.330
I must be boring you.

02:03.490 --> 02:04.360
I understand.

02:04.760 --> 02:06.380
I love collecting all sorts of stones,

02:06.380 --> 02:09.120
and I like to tinker
with clever little mechanisms.

02:09.120 --> 02:11.120
Perhaps I can make a bookcase for you

02:11.400 --> 02:13.120
that categorizes your books,

02:13.120 --> 02:14.590
making them easy to organize and find.

02:14.590 --> 02:16.350
It also comes apart
so you can carry it with you.

02:16.350 --> 02:17.790
If you truly can make such a thing,

02:17.790 --> 02:19.590
you'll do me a tremendous favor.

02:20.240 --> 02:22.700
Since you're fond of ingenious mechanisms,

02:23.590 --> 02:25.150
I believe I have a few books

02:25.150 --> 02:27.310
on long-lost ancient craftsmanship.

02:28.510 --> 02:29.560
I could never make sense of them,

02:29.560 --> 02:30.910
so they've been gathering dust.

02:30.910 --> 02:32.100
If you don't mind,

02:32.310 --> 02:34.079
consider them my gift to you.

02:34.230 --> 02:36.360
Then I'll gladly accept them, Yuanji.

04:04.010 --> 04:08.150
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:08.560 --> 04:11.070
[Episode 5]

04:11.150 --> 04:12.750
Trinkets, pretty little ornaments!

04:11.750 --> 04:14.110
[Xiyue Restaurant]

04:13.520 --> 04:14.240
Take a look.

04:18.579 --> 04:20.940
[Jing Lan, Owner of Xiyue Restaurant]

04:22.670 --> 04:24.130
I heard that two years ago,

04:24.510 --> 04:26.360
you and Liu Da,
the owner of Qile Tavern on East Street,

04:26.360 --> 04:27.020
had a fight.

04:27.560 --> 04:28.510
You took his chef

04:28.510 --> 04:29.770
and injured his staff.

04:30.240 --> 04:30.870
In the end,

04:31.510 --> 04:34.680
the Capital Prefecture
suspended your business for three months

04:34.680 --> 04:35.540
as punishment.

04:36.190 --> 04:36.870
Bull...

04:37.720 --> 04:38.600
Bullshit.

04:38.850 --> 04:39.800
That lover of Liu Da's

04:39.800 --> 04:41.000
is related to that Capital Prefect

04:41.000 --> 04:42.720
through God knows
how many branches of the family.

04:42.720 --> 04:44.159
The Capital Prefect abused his authority

04:44.159 --> 04:45.750
to rule against me unfairly!

04:45.750 --> 04:46.560
What a jerk!

04:46.720 --> 04:47.690
What a coincidence.

04:47.690 --> 04:50.020
I've already killed the Capital Prefect.

04:50.870 --> 04:52.680
You're Xiao Wuyi,
the heir of

04:53.560 --> 04:54.490
Prince Jing'an?

04:55.830 --> 04:56.600
Your Highness, these are

04:56.600 --> 05:00.060
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft's ledgers
you asked for.

05:00.310 --> 05:00.910
Burn them.

05:01.190 --> 05:02.320
Yes, Your Highness.

05:03.410 --> 05:03.850
I...

05:05.630 --> 05:07.000
Actually, you've known

05:07.000 --> 05:11.000
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft's
true identity all along, right?

05:12.440 --> 05:14.170
From this moment on, you don't.

05:14.800 --> 05:16.000
No matter who asks you about

05:16.000 --> 05:17.920
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

05:17.920 --> 05:19.580
you know absolutely nothing.

05:19.920 --> 05:20.650
Understood?

05:22.600 --> 05:24.630
You're from Luzhou in the Northwest.

05:24.630 --> 05:25.800
You have a younger brother

05:25.800 --> 05:27.660
serving in the Pang'e Army there.

05:27.830 --> 05:29.310
You've lost contact with him for years,

05:29.310 --> 05:30.680
and you've been
searching for him ever since,

05:30.680 --> 05:32.600
not knowing whether he's alive or dead.

05:32.600 --> 05:34.659
I'll find a way to help you locate him.

05:35.510 --> 05:36.970
Take these silver ingots,

05:37.240 --> 05:38.550
and you'll work for me from now on.

05:38.550 --> 05:40.480
I need a place like your restaurant

05:40.830 --> 05:42.510
to gather intelligence
from across the city.

05:42.510 --> 05:44.040
As for whether this restaurant

05:44.040 --> 05:46.040
belongs to you or someone else,

05:46.040 --> 05:46.770
I don't care.

05:47.560 --> 05:49.020
All the profits are yours.

05:50.550 --> 05:51.450
Say yes already.

05:51.450 --> 05:52.310
Don't be a fool.

05:52.630 --> 05:54.090
With His Highness backing you up
from now on,

05:54.090 --> 05:55.870
do you still need to
be afraid of that Liu fellow?

05:55.870 --> 05:58.830
Jing Lan is at Your Highness's command.

06:00.120 --> 06:01.630
Good. From today on,

06:02.360 --> 06:04.040
your restaurant will
host storytelling performances.

06:04.040 --> 06:05.370
Hire more storytellers

06:05.390 --> 06:07.390
and have them tell the stories well.

06:11.270 --> 06:12.560
Crown Prince Wenxi.

06:13.390 --> 06:14.590
Phoenix Heart Token?

06:15.040 --> 06:17.440
Does anyone still believe such old rumors?

06:28.310 --> 06:29.040
Understood.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.620
Ask nothing, say nothing.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.000
Record everyone
who asks about the whereabouts

06:33.000 --> 06:34.530
of the Phoenix Heart Token.

06:34.800 --> 06:35.930
Yes, Your Highness.

06:36.630 --> 06:37.490
One more thing.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.430
The Secondary Consort
got up early this morning

06:51.430 --> 06:53.430
and visited the Princess's
and the Consort's quarters.

06:53.430 --> 06:54.480
She drank two bowls of duck soup,

06:54.480 --> 06:56.000
and the Consort gave her two books.

06:56.000 --> 06:57.850
Just now, she followed
the Consort and Young Master Ziqi

06:57.850 --> 06:59.580
to Madam Ruisheng's quarters.

07:00.750 --> 07:03.010
She's certainly making herself at home—

07:03.600 --> 07:05.200
eating and accepting gifts.

07:05.600 --> 07:07.800
Isn't it because Your Highness instructed
the household earlier

07:07.800 --> 07:09.060
to treat Lady Xie well?

07:09.190 --> 07:11.310
I just don't see
what you're gaining from this.

07:11.310 --> 07:12.510
You married a troublemaker,

07:12.510 --> 07:13.510
and you've spent so much money

07:13.510 --> 07:14.920
buying the Xiyue Restaurant for her,

07:14.920 --> 07:16.230
just so no one would discover

07:16.230 --> 07:17.630
that she's
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

07:17.630 --> 07:19.960
How much private savings do you even have?

07:20.430 --> 07:21.690
Do you want to be caned?

07:24.150 --> 07:24.800
Your Highness,

07:24.800 --> 07:26.750
the bodies
of Lady Xie's maid and secret guard

07:26.750 --> 07:27.860
have been brought back.

07:27.860 --> 07:28.330
Good.

07:28.870 --> 07:30.160
Let's go see what Xie Jiayu looks like

07:30.160 --> 07:32.220
after Ruisheng's gotten hold of her.

07:33.800 --> 07:34.480
Ow! Ow! Ow!

07:35.260 --> 07:36.750
Ruisheng, I can't take it anymore!

07:36.750 --> 07:38.330
This is the Yongquan acupoint.

07:38.330 --> 07:39.500
If this spot hurts,

07:39.530 --> 07:41.530
it means you have poor circulation.

07:41.680 --> 07:43.800
This is
the Foot Yangming Stomach Meridian.

07:43.800 --> 07:46.730
Your digestion
hasn't been very good either, has it?

07:49.360 --> 07:50.680
Yuanji, Yuanji, save me!

07:50.680 --> 07:52.310
Bear with it a little longer, Jiayu.

07:52.310 --> 07:54.120
It hurts now,
but once the massage is done,

07:54.120 --> 07:55.520
you'll feel much better.

07:56.159 --> 07:57.290
Consort, you didn't

07:57.720 --> 08:00.800
go to bed until after midnight again
last night, did you?

08:00.800 --> 08:02.460
-I...
-If you keep doing that,

08:02.800 --> 08:05.600
don't expect me to
make you any more calming tonic.

08:08.690 --> 08:09.680
Sisters,

08:09.870 --> 08:12.000
I never imagined you two were so close.

08:12.110 --> 08:13.080
What?

08:13.100 --> 08:15.040
Did you also believe the rumors outside

08:15.040 --> 08:17.010
that we're constantly
at each other's throats?

08:17.010 --> 08:17.890
No, no.

08:18.070 --> 08:19.870
When I gave birth to Ziqi,

08:19.870 --> 08:22.240
it was Consort
who took care of me personally.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.950
All these years, while I've been away
with the army,

08:23.950 --> 08:25.720
she's been raising Ziqi for me.

08:26.320 --> 08:29.000
If you ask who in this household
I'm closest to,

08:29.270 --> 08:30.270
it's not the Heir,

08:30.550 --> 08:31.140
but

08:32.059 --> 08:32.789
his consort.

08:33.030 --> 08:34.630
Even my monthly letters home

08:35.190 --> 08:37.120
were addressed to Madam Ruisheng.

08:39.200 --> 08:40.659
Impressive, impressive.

08:40.840 --> 08:43.549
Xiao Wuyi, you're really something.

08:43.630 --> 08:45.200
You are as skilled at leading an army

08:45.200 --> 08:47.260
as you are at running your household.

08:48.030 --> 08:50.310
Secondary Consort, His Highness the Heir
wishes to see you.

08:50.310 --> 08:51.640
The Heir wants to see me?

08:52.360 --> 08:53.030
Xiao Wuyi,

08:53.150 --> 08:55.150
you've finally rescued me for once.

08:55.480 --> 08:57.130
I'll take my leave first, Sisters.

08:57.130 --> 08:57.760
Excuse me.

09:03.840 --> 09:06.600
The Heir has specifically instructed you

09:06.600 --> 09:09.160
to help nurse
the Secondary Consort's health?

09:09.160 --> 09:09.970
Yes.

09:10.750 --> 09:12.750
He really has gone to great lengths.

09:13.750 --> 09:15.150
Why did you bring me here?

09:15.550 --> 09:16.480
Such a beautiful place...

09:16.480 --> 09:17.750
A place this beautiful

09:18.240 --> 09:20.640
is naturally the best for killing someone.

09:21.030 --> 09:22.550
Oh, I'm so scared.

09:24.510 --> 09:26.170
You're that certain I wouldn't hurt you?

09:26.170 --> 09:28.330
Ruisheng and Yuanji are both good people.

09:28.330 --> 09:30.360
If they haven't teamed up to poison you,

09:30.360 --> 09:31.560
that means you're...

09:32.150 --> 09:33.410
not that bad after all.

09:38.840 --> 09:39.700
This is for you.

09:41.460 --> 09:42.990
This is Cang'er's hairpin.

09:43.720 --> 09:45.910
Your maid and the secret guard

09:46.360 --> 09:47.360
are buried there.

10:05.270 --> 10:06.630
When Beifu soldiers die in battle,

10:06.630 --> 10:07.750
if their bodies are recovered,

10:07.750 --> 10:09.960
they should be respectfully dressed
and buried under a tree.

10:09.960 --> 10:11.760
That's our military tradition.

10:12.510 --> 10:14.240
They were your loyal servants.

10:14.240 --> 10:17.240
They deserved the same honor
for sacrificing for you.

10:19.520 --> 10:20.850
Carve their names on it.

10:29.550 --> 10:30.270
Cang'er,

10:31.750 --> 10:32.680
my secret guard,

10:34.870 --> 10:35.510
I'm sorry.

10:36.960 --> 10:38.240
I got you both killed.

10:39.530 --> 10:40.930
If there's another life,

10:42.390 --> 10:43.790
don't be servants again.

10:45.370 --> 10:46.670
May you become hawks,

10:47.600 --> 10:48.930
soaring across the sky.

10:50.360 --> 10:51.760
Even if there are storms,

10:52.960 --> 10:54.890
you'll know no hunger or hardship.

10:59.960 --> 11:01.610
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

11:02.320 --> 11:04.120
Your Highness, a letter for you.

11:11.000 --> 11:13.360
My Lady, it's from Mr. Jing
of Xiyue Restaurant.

11:13.360 --> 11:15.080
He said someone went to the restaurant

11:15.080 --> 11:17.070
looking for the Young Master of Miraculous Craft
to discuss business.

11:17.070 --> 11:19.800
What did you just deliver
to Lady Xie's quarters?

11:20.270 --> 11:23.330
It was a letter from Xiyue Restaurant
for Her Highness.

11:24.270 --> 11:26.200
A legend has long circulated
across the realm—

11:26.200 --> 11:30.080
"When the Phoenix Heart Token appears,
peace shall be restored in the world."

11:30.080 --> 11:33.720
It's said that Empress Wenxi's child
never actually died.

11:33.940 --> 11:35.520
Once the Phoenix Heart Token resurfaces,

11:35.520 --> 11:38.210
Crown Prince Wenxi
will reappear in the world

11:38.400 --> 11:39.710
and unite the realm.

11:39.840 --> 11:42.510
Ladies and gentlemen, make yourselves
comfortable with some tea...

11:42.510 --> 11:45.630
Mr. Jing, you're looking for
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft?

11:45.630 --> 11:46.910
Do you still remember

11:47.120 --> 11:48.550
Mr. Xiao, who asked you to design
the repeating crossbow

11:48.550 --> 11:49.790
last time?

11:50.000 --> 11:51.510
Why is it about
the repeating crossbow again?

11:51.510 --> 11:52.460
Is there no end to this?

11:52.460 --> 11:53.870
This time it's not about the crossbow.

11:53.870 --> 11:55.000
It's about Mr. Xiao.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.790
He owes me a lot of money.

11:57.080 --> 11:57.910
Food on credit,

11:57.910 --> 11:58.870
drinks on credit—

11:58.870 --> 12:00.390
at this rate, he's going to

12:00.390 --> 12:01.780
bankrupt my restaurant.

12:01.780 --> 12:02.710
I need to sue him.

12:03.790 --> 12:04.840
Really?

12:05.390 --> 12:07.630
I remember he was quite a big spender
when he came

12:07.630 --> 12:09.690
to buy the crossbow from me last time.

12:10.030 --> 12:12.320
Yeah, well, who knows?

12:12.840 --> 12:14.630
Anyway, he owes me a lot of money.

12:14.630 --> 12:15.910
I'm going to sue him right now.

12:15.910 --> 12:16.600
But I...

12:16.720 --> 12:19.000
I don't quite remember what he looks like.

12:19.000 --> 12:20.600
Could you draw me a portrait of him?

12:20.600 --> 12:22.000
He owes you a fortune,

12:22.020 --> 12:24.350
yet you don't remember what he looks like?

12:26.480 --> 12:27.540
You might not know,

12:27.910 --> 12:28.960
but I can never remember people's faces.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.450
I really can't tell faces apart.

12:30.450 --> 12:31.790
Besides, those wealthy young masters

12:31.790 --> 12:33.720
all dress about the same.

12:33.760 --> 12:34.670
They all look alike too,

12:34.670 --> 12:35.790
with their fair, delicate features.

12:35.790 --> 12:37.650
I honestly can't tell them apart.

12:38.840 --> 12:40.550
Then what about all the staff
in your restaurant?

12:40.550 --> 12:41.670
Are they all bad at recognizing faces too?

12:41.670 --> 12:44.550
Not all of them are,

12:44.550 --> 12:46.980
but none of them can paint.

12:47.440 --> 12:49.240
Recognizing faces is one thing;

12:49.340 --> 12:50.870
being able to draw them is another.

12:50.870 --> 12:51.790
You

12:51.790 --> 12:53.600
and our restaurant go way back.

12:54.030 --> 12:55.150
Please help me out.

12:56.150 --> 12:56.720
Alright.

12:57.480 --> 12:59.410
Young Master of Miraculous Craft?

13:01.010 --> 13:03.300
Why does that title sound so familiar?

13:04.600 --> 13:05.930
Repeating crossbow...

13:07.510 --> 13:08.310
Could it be...

13:09.510 --> 13:11.770
Mr. Jing really knows how to spin a story.

13:12.030 --> 13:13.360
We've got the portrait.

13:20.320 --> 13:21.750
Did Xie Jiayu suspect anything?

13:21.750 --> 13:22.440
Not yet.

13:25.120 --> 13:26.790
Start the investigation
from within the palace.

13:26.790 --> 13:28.480
And check the students
at the Imperial Academy

13:28.480 --> 13:30.480
and see if anyone matches this face.

13:30.720 --> 13:34.320
Your Highness suspects
Grand Tutor Xie and the Empress Dowager?

13:35.750 --> 13:37.550
I hope I'm just overthinking it.

13:47.390 --> 13:48.270
Did you know

13:49.030 --> 13:50.960
Xie Jiayu is
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

13:50.960 --> 13:54.040
who makes and sells ingenious devices
through Xiyue Restaurant?

13:54.040 --> 13:56.040
I've never heard that title before.

13:56.850 --> 13:59.850
But Jiayu is indeed skilled at
making mechanical devices.

13:59.850 --> 14:01.780
She even made me a portable bookcase.

14:01.780 --> 14:04.550
If she's been secretly selling
small items in the market,

14:04.550 --> 14:05.630
it's not surprising.

14:05.630 --> 14:07.790
The repeating crossbow
that caused the Beifu soldiers

14:07.790 --> 14:08.960
to die in vain

14:09.510 --> 14:12.240
was made
by the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

14:12.480 --> 14:14.080
I found a repeating crossbow

14:14.080 --> 14:15.270
in Xie Jiayu's dowry chest.

14:15.270 --> 14:16.530
I've compared the two.

14:17.200 --> 14:18.470
Its size, design, and mechanism

14:18.470 --> 14:19.510
are exactly the same.

14:19.510 --> 14:20.870
She must have had an ulterior motive

14:20.870 --> 14:22.320
for marrying into the household.

14:22.320 --> 14:23.630
She cannot be allowed near Ziqi.

14:23.630 --> 14:25.100
You and Mother must be careful as well.

14:25.100 --> 14:27.030
Get rid of that bookcase she gave you.

14:27.030 --> 14:29.360
The Heir asked for this marriage himself.

14:29.360 --> 14:30.940
It wasn't what Jiayu wanted.

14:30.940 --> 14:32.270
If you are worried, Yao,

14:32.420 --> 14:34.050
why don't you ask the Heir directly?

14:34.050 --> 14:35.170
And say what to him?

14:35.910 --> 14:39.110
He's probably already been bewitched
by this evil woman!

14:41.720 --> 14:44.050
Young Master Yao and the Consort...

14:46.390 --> 14:47.750
Careful! Watch out!

14:47.750 --> 14:48.480
Watch out!

14:51.510 --> 14:52.240
Are you okay?

14:54.000 --> 14:54.840
Come with me!

14:55.670 --> 14:56.510
No, Yao.

14:56.600 --> 14:57.510
-Yao.
-Move!

14:57.670 --> 14:59.120
-Ziqi.
-What did I do?

14:59.120 --> 14:59.790
Are you okay, Ziqi?

14:59.790 --> 15:00.520
-Yao.
-Move!

15:01.360 --> 15:01.910
Let's go.

15:01.910 --> 15:03.240
-Let go of me!
-Let's go.

15:05.550 --> 15:06.410
Your Highness.

15:06.750 --> 15:08.790
Young Master Yao claims
the Secondary Consort tried to harm Ziqi.

15:08.790 --> 15:11.550
He's taken the matter
all the way to the ancestral hall.

15:11.550 --> 15:13.150
Alchemy was popular in the former dynasty,

15:13.150 --> 15:15.750
and that's when fireworks were
first created.

15:15.870 --> 15:17.840
In addition to saltpeter,
sulfur, and charcoal,

15:17.840 --> 15:20.040
you can add copper, iron, cotton,
and other materials

15:20.040 --> 15:21.600
to produce different colors.

15:21.600 --> 15:23.600
The fireworks I make sell very well.

15:24.790 --> 15:25.480
Forget it.

15:25.480 --> 15:27.080
You wouldn't understand
even if I explained.

15:27.080 --> 15:28.280
Let me put it this way.

15:28.630 --> 15:29.840
If I really wanted to hurt someone,

15:29.840 --> 15:30.910
I wouldn't make it so complicated.

15:30.910 --> 15:33.110
A little more of one ingredient,
or a little less of another—

15:33.110 --> 15:35.390
and I could make sure
no one here would survive,

15:35.390 --> 15:36.320
including you!

15:36.870 --> 15:39.030
So you admit you've hurt people.

15:39.030 --> 15:40.150
I can hurt people,

15:40.350 --> 15:41.880
but that doesn't mean I did.

15:41.960 --> 15:43.690
You've already harmed people.

15:43.810 --> 15:46.480
You're the Young Master of Miraculous Craft,
aren't you?

15:46.480 --> 15:48.480
My Beifu soldiers were killed by...

15:49.790 --> 15:50.440
Brother!

15:56.200 --> 15:57.930
Consort, take Ziqi away first.

15:58.080 --> 15:59.010
Jiayu, go first.

15:59.550 --> 16:01.360
I have something to say to my brother.

16:01.360 --> 16:02.670
Ziqi, let's go.

16:04.600 --> 16:05.150
Go.

16:05.320 --> 16:06.250
I'm not leaving.

16:07.510 --> 16:09.750
What exactly did I do
to all of you?

16:10.510 --> 16:12.510
It was the repeating crossbow you designed

16:12.510 --> 16:14.770
that killed 30,000 of my Beifu soldiers.

16:20.840 --> 16:21.480
Brother!

16:31.630 --> 16:33.480
And you're still covering for her?

16:33.480 --> 16:35.210
You've been so blinded by lust!

16:36.080 --> 16:36.720
Xie Jiayu,

16:37.670 --> 16:39.570
you say you didn't intend to
harm Ziqi today.

16:39.570 --> 16:41.230
I won't argue with you on that.

16:42.150 --> 16:45.610
But what about the souls
of my 30,000 innocent Beifu soldiers?

16:46.030 --> 16:48.290
Dare you say
it has nothing to do with you?

16:49.310 --> 16:52.110
It was the flawed repeating crossbow
you designed

16:52.470 --> 16:55.800
that caused 30,000 Beifu soldiers
to be nearly wiped out.

16:57.440 --> 17:00.700
Fortunately, Wuyi held on
until reinforcements arrived.

17:01.880 --> 17:04.510
Dare you say you knew nothing about it?

17:05.680 --> 17:08.079
What exactly was your Xie family plotting?

17:17.119 --> 17:19.380
Impossible. There must be some mistake.

17:20.030 --> 17:20.750
Xiao Wuyi.

17:26.880 --> 17:27.680
I clearly...

17:28.680 --> 17:31.280
I clearly designed it
for a noble young master.

17:33.720 --> 17:35.880
Don't worry,
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

17:35.880 --> 17:39.080
will definitely design
the repeating crossbow you want.

17:39.440 --> 17:41.350
He only said
he was taking it to a literary gathering

17:41.350 --> 17:44.080
and just needed it
to look good and intimidating.

17:46.590 --> 17:48.050
Which noble young master?

17:50.110 --> 17:51.480
He said his name was Xiao Sheng.

17:51.480 --> 17:52.400
Xiao Sheng?

17:53.770 --> 17:54.530
Xiao Wuyi,

17:55.150 --> 17:59.010
she said you were the one who commissioned
the design. Do you admit it?

18:02.000 --> 18:03.660
Why are you called Xiao Sheng?

18:05.030 --> 18:06.490
Isn't your name Xiao Wuyi?

18:06.790 --> 18:08.320
Xiao Sheng is my birth name.

18:09.120 --> 18:10.520
Wuyi is my courtesy name.

18:11.720 --> 18:14.050
Ever since I went to the battlefield
at 14,

18:14.200 --> 18:16.400
no one has called me Xiao Sheng anymore.

18:17.400 --> 18:18.200
No wonder.

18:19.750 --> 18:21.000
No wonder when Qing Long and Yan Yue

18:21.000 --> 18:23.000
came to Xiyue Restaurant to find me,

18:23.420 --> 18:26.150
they got upset the moment
I mentioned Xiao Sheng.

18:28.350 --> 18:30.010
But that still doesn't add up.

18:30.160 --> 18:31.620
It wasn't you who came to find me then.

18:31.620 --> 18:34.200
But he looked like a pampered young maste
at first glance.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.600
If it's really as you say,

18:35.790 --> 18:38.740
then he disguised his identity
from the very beginning.

18:38.740 --> 18:41.130
So who was really behind the deaths
of my 30,000 Beifu soldiers,

18:41.130 --> 18:42.690
using you as their pawn?

18:43.270 --> 18:44.680
And who else knew

18:45.640 --> 18:48.570
that you'd designed
the flawed repeating crossbow?

18:56.030 --> 18:57.560
How would he know my father?

19:21.680 --> 19:24.080
The first lesson I learned
after growing up

19:24.400 --> 19:26.930
was that life doesn't always
give us a choice.

19:26.960 --> 19:29.510
You must be the pawn.

19:32.150 --> 19:32.590
Jiayu.

19:33.030 --> 19:34.160
Where are you going?

19:38.590 --> 19:40.720
You really knew about this all along.

19:41.840 --> 19:43.510
And yet, you're still protecting her?

19:43.510 --> 19:45.510
I'm sure you can see it too, Brother.

19:45.790 --> 19:47.590
Xie Jiayu knew nothing about it.

19:47.600 --> 19:49.030
But if this matter gets out,

19:49.030 --> 19:50.880
wouldn't it chill the hearts
of the soldiers?

19:50.880 --> 19:52.920
And this Xie woman, with her honeyed words
and deceptive charm—

19:52.920 --> 19:53.880
before she even entered the household,

19:53.880 --> 19:56.110
she'd already harmed
so many Beifu soldiers.

19:56.110 --> 19:58.770
Don't those soldiers
deserve to know the truth?

19:59.480 --> 20:00.790
Does erecting a monument mean

20:00.790 --> 20:03.070
that my soldiers' grievances are settled?

20:03.070 --> 20:04.070
Of course not.

20:06.790 --> 20:08.390
Then what do you intend to do?

20:10.270 --> 20:12.200
You'll know soon enough, Brother.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.030
Take care.

20:16.030 --> 20:17.030
Look at this cloth.

20:17.030 --> 20:18.490
You have a really good eye.

20:34.480 --> 20:35.540
-Father.
-Father.

20:35.830 --> 20:36.890
-Mother.
-Mother.

20:38.310 --> 20:39.110
Good, good.

20:40.150 --> 20:41.010
Darling, look.

20:41.750 --> 20:43.400
Have you ever seen Yaoyao

20:43.680 --> 20:46.030
so gentle and graceful?

20:46.750 --> 20:47.510
Heir,

20:47.880 --> 20:50.230
has my daughter caused you any trouble?

20:51.680 --> 20:53.000
Jiayu has been wonderful.

20:53.000 --> 20:55.200
Everyone in the household is fond of her.

20:55.200 --> 20:58.200
My daughter might not be
exceptionally outstanding,

20:58.200 --> 20:59.510
but I never imagined

20:59.990 --> 21:01.720
marrying her off in such haste,

21:02.160 --> 21:04.510
much less as a secondary consort.

21:04.830 --> 21:06.030
To be honest,

21:06.790 --> 21:09.110
I didn't expect this marriage
to actually happen.

21:09.110 --> 21:11.510
Since Jiayu entered our household
for the sake of the realm,

21:11.510 --> 21:13.160
our family will naturally treat her well.

21:13.160 --> 21:14.510
Please rest assured, Princess.

21:14.510 --> 21:15.160
Mother,

21:15.590 --> 21:17.880
he knows I enjoy
making mechanical devices,

21:17.880 --> 21:20.160
so he set aside a space
in the household for me

21:20.160 --> 21:21.680
to make the things I like.

21:22.310 --> 21:23.590
The wedding was so rushed,

21:23.590 --> 21:26.320
and I didn't have time
to take many things with me.

21:26.400 --> 21:27.350
Now that I'm back,

21:27.350 --> 21:28.920
I'd also like to take my books
on mechanisms

21:28.920 --> 21:30.110
and tools with me.

21:30.860 --> 21:31.510
Heir,

21:33.110 --> 21:34.640
go with Nanxing to my study

21:34.790 --> 21:36.180
and take all my blueprints.

21:36.180 --> 21:37.590
Don't leave a single one behind.

21:37.590 --> 21:40.720
I still have something I want to say
to Father and Mother.

21:57.510 --> 21:58.310
Yaoyao,

21:58.890 --> 21:59.950
what are you doing?

22:00.650 --> 22:03.850
Are you going to help Xiao Wuyi
improve military weapons?

22:07.440 --> 22:09.840
Then do you know
what you are doing, Father?

22:10.030 --> 22:11.720
Thirty thousand Beifu soldiers—

22:11.720 --> 22:13.450
that's thirty thousand lives!

22:14.960 --> 22:16.110
Father, you deliberately
arranged for someone to come to me

22:16.110 --> 22:18.510
and commission
the repeating crossbow, didn't you?

22:18.510 --> 22:21.110
I once saw the man
who called himself Xiao Sheng

22:21.750 --> 22:23.610
entering and leaving your study.

22:26.880 --> 22:28.200
What does that prove?

22:28.610 --> 22:30.670
That indeed doesn't prove anything.

22:31.350 --> 22:33.210
But now I understand, in my heart,

22:34.200 --> 22:35.790
why you encouraged me to design

22:35.790 --> 22:37.480
the repeating crossbow back then.

22:37.480 --> 22:38.960
I even told you

22:38.960 --> 22:39.890
about its flaws.

22:40.790 --> 22:41.680
Not long after,

22:42.160 --> 22:43.640
that man calling himself Xiao Sheng

22:43.640 --> 22:46.110
came looking for
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft to buy it.

22:46.110 --> 22:46.720
Father,

22:47.590 --> 22:50.720
can you truly say none of this
had anything to do with you?

23:08.350 --> 23:09.480
These three kowtows

23:10.240 --> 23:12.570
are to thank you and Mother
for raising me.

23:12.830 --> 23:14.490
If you had sacrificed only me,

23:14.920 --> 23:16.320
I could have understood—

23:16.480 --> 23:18.130
you simply stood on a different side

23:18.130 --> 23:19.090
and gave me up.

23:20.310 --> 23:21.640
But what you've done now

23:22.400 --> 23:24.280
is unworthy of the honor and integrity

23:24.280 --> 23:26.080
expected of a great noble house.

23:29.990 --> 23:31.840
Then what are you going to do?

23:33.110 --> 23:34.170
Are you going to...

23:38.120 --> 23:39.450
expose me, your father?

23:41.790 --> 23:42.400
On the night of my wedding,

23:42.400 --> 23:43.310
I couldn't do any of the things

23:43.310 --> 23:44.400
you asked me to do,

23:44.760 --> 23:46.020
nor will I ever do them.

23:46.270 --> 23:48.750
The repeating crossbow
created a debt of lives.

23:48.750 --> 23:49.590
If one day

23:50.030 --> 23:52.630
the Beifu soldiers
come and ask me to pay for it,

23:53.000 --> 23:54.200
then, as the daughter you have raised

23:54.200 --> 23:55.350
all these years,

23:56.400 --> 23:58.920
I will repay that debt
with my life in your stead

23:58.920 --> 24:00.250
and have no complaints.

24:00.590 --> 24:02.520
But what this world is really like,

24:03.110 --> 24:04.310
I will see for myself.

24:05.350 --> 24:06.590
And the road ahead,

24:07.750 --> 24:09.150
I will choose for myself.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.680
So will Mao.

24:18.200 --> 24:19.330
Mother, forgive me.

24:19.750 --> 24:21.150
I really have no appetite

24:21.590 --> 24:23.250
for this homecoming banquet.

24:36.750 --> 24:37.950
We'll take our leave.

24:46.030 --> 24:46.680
Darling,

24:47.720 --> 24:48.780
eat while it's hot.

25:02.590 --> 25:05.750
About how many people
are there in the city?

25:06.590 --> 25:08.050
Over 200,000 households.

25:08.830 --> 25:10.510
Every Lantern Festival,

25:11.160 --> 25:13.290
the city hosts its largest gathering.

25:14.450 --> 25:16.450
The streets are packed with people.

25:17.710 --> 25:19.370
Would there be 30,000 people?

25:23.440 --> 25:24.370
There should be.

25:26.340 --> 25:27.410
That many people?

25:31.270 --> 25:33.270
That many people died because of me.

25:40.040 --> 25:41.330
I need some time alone.

25:46.510 --> 25:47.440
Qing Long, Yan Yue,

25:47.440 --> 25:49.480
stay close.
Don't let anything happen to her.

25:49.480 --> 25:50.140
-Yes.
-Yes.

26:06.900 --> 26:10.720
[Chengyi Hall]

26:09.420 --> 26:10.350
Excuse me, Shopkeeper.

26:10.350 --> 26:11.030
Who is it?

26:12.310 --> 26:13.510
-We're closed.
-Sir.

26:14.620 --> 26:16.510
Sir, I'd like a bag of pear blossom candy.

26:16.510 --> 26:17.170
Sorry to bother you.

26:17.170 --> 26:18.300
Come back tomorrow.

26:18.310 --> 26:20.160
My sister is in a bad mood today.

26:20.360 --> 26:22.270
She's always loved
your pear blossom candy.

26:22.270 --> 26:24.130
I'll pay 10 times the usual price.

26:45.640 --> 26:47.500
What's the point of burning them?

26:49.960 --> 26:51.420
Are you here to laugh at me?

26:51.550 --> 26:52.880
Why would I laugh at you?

26:53.510 --> 26:55.270
Laugh at how your own father used you

26:55.270 --> 26:57.070
to bring ruin upon my Beifu Army?

26:58.030 --> 27:00.000
You're the commander of the Beifu Army.

27:00.000 --> 27:01.400
Aren't you angry with me?

27:02.160 --> 27:03.890
Though it wasn't my intention,

27:04.030 --> 27:06.360
I did cause
the deaths of so many soldiers.

27:06.920 --> 27:08.720
Why am I bothering with an idiot?

27:09.830 --> 27:10.920
You're an idiot.

27:12.640 --> 27:14.500
Why do you have so many questions?

27:14.880 --> 27:17.550
There is no good or evil inherent
in a technique; it is only a technique.

27:17.550 --> 27:19.010
If I had to blame everyone,

27:19.110 --> 27:19.880
besides you,

27:20.000 --> 27:21.680
I'd have to start with Lu Ban.

27:22.720 --> 27:23.920
What does he have to do with this?

27:23.920 --> 27:26.050
If he hadn't invented all those tools,

27:26.270 --> 27:28.470
the art of mechanical carpentry
would never have come into being.

27:28.470 --> 27:29.270
And after him,

27:29.400 --> 27:31.640
I would also blame Mozi,
who pioneered mechanical engineering.

27:31.640 --> 27:32.640
Tracing back even further,

27:32.640 --> 27:35.110
there's Zhang Hui,
grandson of the Yellow Emperor.

27:35.110 --> 27:36.920
Legend says he invented the bow and arrow.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.030
Don't you want to place blame?

27:38.030 --> 27:39.550
Every wrong has its source.

27:39.550 --> 27:40.680
Bring them all to me.

27:40.960 --> 27:43.270
I want to settle accounts with
each of them properly.

27:43.270 --> 27:45.640
As for you, at most, you're an accomplice.

27:51.550 --> 27:52.610
From Chengyi Hall?

27:52.680 --> 27:54.880
It must've been Mao who told you, right?

28:00.790 --> 28:02.000
Mao gave this to me.

28:02.350 --> 28:03.610
Mao treats me the best.

28:10.070 --> 28:10.720
Xiao Wuyi,

28:11.510 --> 28:12.720
you and your family

28:13.270 --> 28:14.870
are not quite what I'd heard.

28:18.070 --> 28:20.070
The night your father sent you here,

28:20.400 --> 28:22.000
what exactly did he tell you?

28:23.510 --> 28:24.400
Let me guess.

28:25.200 --> 28:26.070
Did he say

28:26.590 --> 28:28.480
that my family commands the Beifu Army

28:28.480 --> 28:30.540
and is bound to rebel sooner or later?

28:30.590 --> 28:32.240
And that, even if only for Li Mao's sake,

28:32.240 --> 28:34.720
you had to marry into this family
to keep an eye on me, right?

28:34.720 --> 28:36.070
How do you know everything?

28:36.070 --> 28:37.130
Are you some kind of demon?

28:37.130 --> 28:38.930
War is waged on the battlefield—

28:39.590 --> 28:40.520
and in the heart.

28:41.960 --> 28:43.360
If only I could see things

28:43.640 --> 28:44.830
as clearly as you do.

28:45.510 --> 28:47.170
I don't understand my father.

28:47.440 --> 28:49.590
Isn't the Beifu Army
guarding the Northern Border?

28:49.590 --> 28:50.660
Why did he do this?

28:52.310 --> 28:54.570
I think you're better off staying a fool.

28:57.190 --> 28:59.730
By the way, there's something serious
I need to tell you.

28:59.730 --> 29:01.320
What serious business
could you possibly have?

29:01.320 --> 29:02.080
Mao is sick.

29:02.430 --> 29:04.350
What? How could he be sick?

29:05.030 --> 29:06.640
There are so many imperial physicians
looking after him.

29:06.640 --> 29:08.170
How could he still get sick?

29:08.750 --> 29:10.160
Is it serious? Take me to the palace now.

29:10.160 --> 29:11.790
The imperial physicians
have already examined him.

29:11.790 --> 29:13.050
It's nothing serious.

29:13.560 --> 29:15.620
He just hasn't had
much of an appetite lately.

29:15.620 --> 29:17.320
He wants you to
make him some hawthorn cakes,

29:17.320 --> 29:19.200
and I'll take them to the palace for him.

29:19.200 --> 29:20.510
Is he really alright?

29:21.070 --> 29:22.320
He just wants some hawthorn cakes?

29:22.320 --> 29:23.480
Why would I lie to you?

29:23.480 --> 29:24.110
Alright.

29:24.310 --> 29:25.710
I'll make them tomorrow.

29:29.350 --> 29:30.000
Xiao Wuyi.

29:31.310 --> 29:33.400
The incident involving the repeating crossbow
was never my intention.

29:33.400 --> 29:34.550
But I owe you an unparalleled weapon

29:34.550 --> 29:37.220
that will let your army
turn defeat into victory,

29:37.220 --> 29:39.030
protect your soldiers
as they charge fearlessly ahead,

29:39.030 --> 29:40.830
and secure the Northern Border.

29:43.240 --> 29:44.200
I give you my word.

29:44.200 --> 29:45.600
I'll definitely make it.

29:45.790 --> 29:47.320
What, you don't believe me?

29:50.440 --> 29:51.030
Okay.

29:52.640 --> 29:53.570
I'll be waiting.

30:01.830 --> 30:04.240
What? Why is he smiling all of a sudden?

30:06.680 --> 30:08.010
Is Prince Qi sick today?

30:08.110 --> 30:09.880
You didn't go to
the palace today, Your Highness.

30:09.880 --> 30:11.590
It was just to
find Xie Jiayu something to do

30:11.590 --> 30:13.700
so she wouldn't sit around
brooding all day.

30:13.700 --> 30:15.700
The pear blossom candy is too sweet.

30:16.400 --> 30:17.670
Go get me a cup of hawthorn juice.

30:17.670 --> 30:19.750
I think you're the one
who wants some hawthorn cakes.

30:19.750 --> 30:20.810
You love sour food.

30:24.640 --> 30:26.830
Your Highness, there's something
I can't figure out.

30:26.830 --> 30:28.550
Given how naive Xie Jiayu is,

30:28.680 --> 30:30.200
she was basically born
to be someone else's pawn.

30:30.200 --> 30:31.160
Grand Tutor Xie went to such great lengths

30:31.160 --> 30:32.350
to marry her to you.

30:32.510 --> 30:33.750
What was he hoping to achieve?

30:33.750 --> 30:34.960
Surely he doesn't actually expect

30:34.960 --> 30:36.750
her to bring back intel from our mansion.

30:36.750 --> 30:39.270
Grand Tutor Xie is a master manipulator.

30:39.790 --> 30:41.250
It's just that the one he's

30:41.480 --> 30:43.410
scheming against isn't Xie Jiayu.

30:43.720 --> 30:44.720
Then who is it?

30:44.790 --> 30:46.940
If you can't figure it out,
go ask Yan Yue.

30:46.940 --> 30:47.920
I'm not asking her.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.380
I'll figure it out myself.

30:51.470 --> 30:53.110
This is the reward
bestowed by His Majesty.

30:53.110 --> 30:56.550
Lu Dayong, you led your men
and refused the reward.

30:57.200 --> 30:58.630
Are you trying to defy the imperial edict?

30:58.630 --> 30:59.990
If I accept the reward,

30:59.220 --> 31:01.660
[Lu Dayong,
Lieutenant General of the Beifu Army]

31:00.620 --> 31:01.400
I'd be betraying

31:01.400 --> 31:03.360
the men who died in vain
at Jiuzhang Plain!

31:03.360 --> 31:04.180
[Feng Wu,
Lieutenant General of the Beifu Army]

31:03.480 --> 31:05.410
Still talking nonsense? Still...

31:05.920 --> 31:06.980
What are you doing?

31:07.300 --> 31:08.260
Are you rebelling?

31:08.260 --> 31:10.020
Step aside! Kneel!

31:14.240 --> 31:14.960
My Beifu soldiers

31:14.960 --> 31:16.490
do not kneel without cause!

31:17.380 --> 31:18.380
Get up, all of you!

31:23.790 --> 31:24.850
Give me the roster.

31:32.110 --> 31:32.910
Feng Zhiyuan.

31:36.880 --> 31:37.920
Fang Shiba.

31:42.790 --> 31:43.590
Cao Xing'an!

31:44.480 --> 31:45.340
Your Highness,

31:46.120 --> 31:47.920
in the battle of Jiuzhang Plain,

31:47.920 --> 31:50.030
why did our 30,000 soldiers die in vain?

31:50.030 --> 31:52.960
At that time, the Directorate of Armaments
rushed out a batch of repeating crossbows.

31:52.960 --> 31:55.840
They said those crossbows
could fire nine arrows in one shot.

31:55.840 --> 31:57.190
But on the battlefield,

31:57.350 --> 31:59.950
the crossbows lost accuracy
after a few shots.

32:00.200 --> 32:01.590
Only last night did we learn

32:01.590 --> 32:03.310
that the one who designed the crossbow

32:03.310 --> 32:05.270
is your newly wedded secondary consort—

32:05.270 --> 32:07.470
Grand Tutor Xie's daughter, Xie Jiayu!

32:08.000 --> 32:09.400
May I ask, Your Highness—

32:09.720 --> 32:11.380
was your marriage to Xie Jiayu

32:11.790 --> 32:14.050
meant to seek peace with the noble clans?

32:14.720 --> 32:16.200
Are you going to participate in
the peace talks with Northern Qin?

32:16.200 --> 32:17.260
Have you forgotten

32:18.070 --> 32:20.590
our blood feud with Northern Qin?

32:20.830 --> 32:21.510
Insolence!

32:21.750 --> 32:22.310
Stop!

32:25.680 --> 32:26.650
Fifty strikes with the military rod.

32:26.650 --> 32:27.180
Yes, sir.

32:27.720 --> 32:29.240
Men, take him away.

32:39.920 --> 32:41.250
Distribute the reward.

32:52.720 --> 32:54.920
-Your Highness, we're incompetent.
-Your Highness.

32:54.920 --> 32:58.680
We still let word about
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft slip out.

32:58.680 --> 33:00.010
Was it Young Master Yao?

33:00.510 --> 33:03.240
Is he displeased
that you haven't punished Lady Xie,

33:03.240 --> 33:04.810
so he deliberately spread
the news within the army?

33:04.810 --> 33:05.330
No.

33:06.310 --> 33:07.640
Maybe it was the Empress Dowager.

33:07.640 --> 33:09.570
Have we found any leads on that impostor

33:09.570 --> 33:10.630
within the palace?

33:10.790 --> 33:11.480
Not yet.

33:12.110 --> 33:12.970
Your Highness,

33:13.590 --> 33:15.920
I'm afraid there are spies
in the army now.

33:16.030 --> 33:17.270
If we don't give the soldiers
an explanation,

33:17.270 --> 33:19.270
the consequences
may not end with you alone.

33:19.270 --> 33:21.470
There might even be a mutiny in the army.

33:26.200 --> 33:28.110
Yuanji. Yuanji.

33:28.350 --> 33:29.010
Wait for me.

33:31.030 --> 33:33.160
Are you going out to buy books, Yuanji?

33:33.200 --> 33:34.110
Can you give me a ride?

33:34.110 --> 33:36.350
Didn't the Heir forbid you from going out?

33:36.350 --> 33:38.480
Why are you in such a hurry?

33:39.480 --> 33:40.920
I want to make some hawthorn cakes,

33:40.920 --> 33:42.720
but we've run out of osmanthus honey,

33:42.720 --> 33:44.580
so I want to sneak out and buy some.

33:44.790 --> 33:45.590
For the Heir?

33:46.310 --> 33:47.070
No.

33:47.310 --> 33:48.510
Why would I give the cakes to him?

33:48.510 --> 33:49.480
I heard from Mother-in-law

33:49.480 --> 33:51.400
that he loves hawthorn cakes the most.

33:51.400 --> 33:53.480
Actually, he likes anything sour.

33:54.420 --> 33:56.150
But I'm not making them for him.

33:56.260 --> 33:58.520
They're for my good friend in the palace.

33:59.110 --> 33:59.880
Li Lejun,

34:00.000 --> 34:01.130
Princess Pingning.

34:01.260 --> 34:02.120
She's been sick

34:02.230 --> 34:04.350
and wants something sour
to whet her appetite.

34:04.350 --> 34:06.610
I wonder how they're doing in the palace.

34:07.240 --> 34:09.900
With so many
imperial physicians and servants,

34:09.960 --> 34:12.030
how could she still be sick
and lose her appetite?

34:12.030 --> 34:14.320
Yuanji, you're
the Empress Dowager's niece.

34:14.320 --> 34:16.150
You must know her better than anyone.

34:16.150 --> 34:18.400
Is Her Majesty easy to get along with?

34:26.389 --> 34:27.840
Yuanji. Yuanji.

34:29.429 --> 34:30.760
What are you thinking about, Yuanji?

34:30.760 --> 34:32.409
You've been lost in thought for so long.

34:32.409 --> 34:33.380
Don't worry.

34:34.150 --> 34:36.659
The Empress Dowager has always
been kind to those useful to her.

34:36.659 --> 34:39.090
And Prince Qi and Princess Pingning

34:39.190 --> 34:40.440
are the most useful people

34:40.440 --> 34:41.440
to her right now.

34:42.110 --> 34:43.150
They'll be fine.

34:44.320 --> 34:45.210
That's a relief.

34:45.210 --> 34:45.770
Get lost.

34:48.550 --> 34:49.110
Scram!

34:51.100 --> 34:51.750
Da?

34:52.280 --> 34:53.340
Stop the carriage.

34:53.840 --> 34:54.840
Get lost now.

34:55.590 --> 34:57.650
A mute, wanting to
join the Imperial Guard?

34:57.650 --> 34:59.070
Do you really think you're worthy of that?

34:59.070 --> 35:00.510
What? I told you to get lost.

34:59.980 --> 35:01.490
[Yue Qingyang,
Commander of the Imperial Guard]

35:00.510 --> 35:01.770
Can't you understand?

35:01.980 --> 35:03.440
Why can't you understand?

35:05.590 --> 35:06.790
You dare fight back? I...

35:06.790 --> 35:07.430
Stop!

35:12.490 --> 35:13.340
Are you okay?

35:16.590 --> 35:17.860
Why are you hitting him?

35:17.860 --> 35:19.880
Everyone admitted to the Imperial Guard

35:19.880 --> 35:21.880
comes from a distinguished family.

35:22.470 --> 35:24.730
Him—a commoner with nothing to his name—

35:24.870 --> 35:27.130
do you really think just anyone can join?

35:27.280 --> 35:29.540
The notice doesn't say mutes can't join,

35:29.720 --> 35:31.780
nor does it say only nobles may apply.

35:32.420 --> 35:33.630
As long as they meet the requirements,

35:33.630 --> 35:34.690
anyone can sign up.

35:35.110 --> 35:36.370
The Imperial Guard embodies
the authority of the throne.

35:36.370 --> 35:37.620
It protects the capital

35:37.620 --> 35:39.280
and safeguards
all the people under the Emperor.

35:39.280 --> 35:40.940
How dare you abuse your power?

35:40.950 --> 35:43.010
You've certainly got a sharp tongue.

35:44.030 --> 35:47.400
If you have the guts,
come argue in my Imperial Guard Office.

35:47.740 --> 35:48.400
Seize them!

35:49.190 --> 35:49.800
Hold on!

35:52.320 --> 35:52.920
Yuanji.

35:54.110 --> 35:56.020
The commanders
of the Imperial Guard mostly

35:56.020 --> 35:56.990
come from powerful noble families.

35:56.990 --> 35:57.800
Better not start a conflict with them.

35:57.800 --> 36:00.630
So it's the ladies
from Prince Jing'an's household.

36:00.630 --> 36:02.590
Young Lord Xiao is truly lucky in love.

36:02.590 --> 36:03.590
I wonder

36:03.590 --> 36:05.440
which two ladies have graced us today.

36:05.440 --> 36:06.400
What's it to you?

36:06.470 --> 36:07.470
Just curious.

36:08.150 --> 36:10.360
I recently heard a story at a restaurant

36:10.440 --> 36:12.030
saying that
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

36:12.030 --> 36:14.540
who caused the death
of 30,000 Beifu soldiers,

36:14.540 --> 36:17.800
is the new secondary consort
of the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

36:17.920 --> 36:20.000
Young Lord Xiao is so romantic

36:20.000 --> 36:21.000
and broad-minded

36:21.070 --> 36:23.550
that he even married
the culprit who caused

36:23.580 --> 36:25.190
the death of the Beifu soldiers.

36:25.190 --> 36:27.250
I just wonder if those Beifu soldiers

36:27.480 --> 36:31.320
could be as forgiving as he is.

36:33.250 --> 36:35.380
That Young Master of Miraculous Craft

36:36.330 --> 36:38.190
wouldn't happen to be you, right?

36:39.480 --> 36:40.030
You...

36:43.630 --> 36:44.430
Who shot that?

36:44.740 --> 36:46.180
W-Who shot the arrow?

36:47.400 --> 36:50.200
Yue Qingyang, instead of
running your mouth here,

36:50.630 --> 36:51.960
you should train your troops more

36:51.960 --> 36:53.510
and focus on your duties!

36:54.110 --> 36:56.230
Then perhaps, when the Prince of Changsha
staged his coup,

36:56.230 --> 36:58.190
your men wouldn't have wet themselves

36:58.190 --> 37:01.720
waiting for our Beifu Army
to march all the way here and save you!

37:02.710 --> 37:03.970
Return to the mansion!

37:09.680 --> 37:10.920
You'll regret this.

37:11.700 --> 37:13.000
Da said that after Mao entered the palace,

37:13.000 --> 37:14.540
he had to find a way
to survive on his own.

37:14.540 --> 37:15.230
He tried to join

37:15.230 --> 37:17.380
the Imperial Guard
just to be closer to Li Mao.

37:17.380 --> 37:18.810
But the Imperial Guard accepts only

37:18.810 --> 37:19.970
nobles or men from respectable families.

37:19.970 --> 37:22.630
He went many times
and was chased away each time.

37:25.710 --> 37:28.110
You did it to be closer to Mao?

37:30.470 --> 37:32.070
"His Highness saved my life.

37:32.470 --> 37:33.670
Naturally, wherever he goes,

37:33.670 --> 37:34.530
I will follow."

37:35.830 --> 37:36.560
In that case,

37:37.550 --> 37:39.480
are you willing to
join the Beifu Army first?

37:39.480 --> 37:42.680
Once I find a chance,
I'll get you into the Imperial Guard.

37:44.590 --> 37:45.360
Get up.

37:51.000 --> 37:52.530
Thank you, Young Lord Xiao.

37:53.230 --> 37:53.840
Let's go.

37:58.400 --> 37:59.110
What?

38:02.550 --> 38:03.950
Who said you could leave?

38:04.510 --> 38:05.360
Hey, what are you doing?

38:05.360 --> 38:06.450
Who said you could leave the mansion?

38:06.450 --> 38:08.180
I warned you on our wedding day—

38:08.320 --> 38:10.360
don't go around causing trouble
under the title of my secondary consort.

38:10.360 --> 38:11.800
How did I cause trouble?

38:11.980 --> 38:13.630
Didn't you ask me to make hawthorn cakes?

38:13.630 --> 38:15.440
How was I supposed to make them
without osmanthus honey?

38:15.440 --> 38:17.000
Mao doesn't like sour food.

38:17.550 --> 38:20.150
And another thing,
I'm not really your secondary consort.

38:20.150 --> 38:22.100
I'm just staying temporarily
at your household.

38:22.100 --> 38:22.900
Temporarily!

38:23.920 --> 38:24.920
If it weren't for Mao...

38:24.920 --> 38:25.670
If it weren't for Mao,

38:25.670 --> 38:27.330
you wouldn't be staying
in this mansion at all.

38:27.330 --> 38:28.920
I don't need you to remind me of that.

38:28.920 --> 38:29.710
Do you think I enjoy

38:29.710 --> 38:31.590
looking at your annoying face every day?

38:31.590 --> 38:33.440
Me? Annoying?

38:33.920 --> 38:34.720
From today on,

38:34.960 --> 38:36.050
you are not allowed to leave the mansion

38:36.050 --> 38:37.280
without my permission.

38:37.280 --> 38:38.740
Yan Yue, keep an eye on her.

38:39.560 --> 38:40.690
Yes, Your Highness.

39:05.230 --> 39:06.830
Say whatever you want to say.

39:07.320 --> 39:09.110
Your Highness is only trying to
protect Lady Xie.

39:09.110 --> 39:10.540
If you'd explained it to her properly,

39:10.540 --> 39:11.940
she might have listened.

39:14.590 --> 39:15.450
I don't need it.

39:16.070 --> 39:17.670
Your Highness, we have news.

39:18.030 --> 39:20.960
The fake Xiao Sheng
was the Empress Dowager's doing.

39:31.200 --> 39:33.530
This indeed looks like my mother's doing.

39:35.550 --> 39:36.480
Grand Tutor Xie,

39:38.290 --> 39:41.020
Mother used
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

39:41.130 --> 39:43.550
to undermine
Xiao Wuyi's influence within the army

39:43.550 --> 39:45.210
and implicate your daughter.

39:45.710 --> 39:48.840
If Xiao Wuyi really
takes action against your daughter,

39:49.880 --> 39:51.280
do you resent Mother for it?

39:51.280 --> 39:54.880
The Empress Dowager wasn't wrong
to curb the Beifu Army's power.

39:59.500 --> 40:00.140
Fine.

40:01.280 --> 40:02.590
Mother wants power,

40:03.440 --> 40:05.770
Xiao Wuyi wants the northern expedition,

40:07.130 --> 40:09.350
you want to preserve
the prestige of the noble clans,

40:09.350 --> 40:11.810
the officials want to
keep their positions,

40:11.960 --> 40:12.760
and Li Mao...

40:16.170 --> 40:17.830
I don't care what Li Mao wants.

40:18.760 --> 40:22.030
You all scheme and plot
right in front of me,

40:22.760 --> 40:24.690
and I don't care about that either.

40:26.400 --> 40:28.030
At most, I have

40:28.030 --> 40:29.440
another year or two left.

40:29.920 --> 40:31.450
As long as I can still stand,

40:31.970 --> 40:34.700
I'll keep holding things together
for all of you.

40:34.800 --> 40:36.460
The day I can no longer hold on,

40:36.950 --> 40:40.350
the realm will be yours
to do with as you please.

40:42.660 --> 40:44.870
I'm tired. You may leave.

40:48.020 --> 40:49.830
I obey, Your Majesty.

40:52.940 --> 40:53.870
Grand Tutor Xie.

41:04.180 --> 41:06.970
You recommended Li Mao.

41:07.950 --> 41:11.070
Valuing friendship and loyalty
is both his strength

41:11.480 --> 41:12.520
and his weakness.

41:14.360 --> 41:16.480
Xiao Wuyi once saved his life.

41:16.990 --> 41:18.110
One careless step,

41:18.520 --> 41:20.730
and he might become Xiao Wuyi's puppet.

41:22.230 --> 41:24.230
I don't want to go to the underworld,

41:24.870 --> 41:26.710
ashamed to face my ancestors,

41:27.960 --> 41:30.760
who would say I chose a ruler
who ruins the country.

41:31.570 --> 41:35.010
For now, I've granted him
the honor of regency,

41:35.430 --> 41:36.310
but if

41:37.690 --> 41:39.550
he fails to meet my expectations,

41:41.660 --> 41:43.660
I will not make him the crown prince.

41:46.960 --> 41:48.280
Do you understand?

41:50.110 --> 41:51.800
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

41:51.800 --> 41:54.570
The crux of this whole game
between Xiao Wuyi and Prince Qi

41:54.570 --> 41:55.900
is my daughter, Jiayu.

41:57.630 --> 41:59.030
Prince Qi is benevolent,

41:59.140 --> 42:01.030
but even the most benevolent person

42:01.030 --> 42:03.570
will have desires once he feels
something is beyond his reach.

42:03.570 --> 42:05.900
And nothing awakens desire

42:06.390 --> 42:08.750
more than watching the woman he loves

42:09.070 --> 42:10.800
drift farther and farther away

42:11.230 --> 42:13.090
while being powerless to stop it.

42:13.280 --> 42:16.810
You married your own daughter
into Prince Jing'an's household

42:18.320 --> 42:20.670
simply to manipulate Li Mao's ambition?

42:22.700 --> 42:23.900
Your Majesty is wise.

42:25.550 --> 42:28.590
You're truly a loyal subject of my realm.

42:44.900 --> 42:45.830
Did you see that?

42:46.840 --> 42:49.040
So these are your master's true colors—

42:49.550 --> 42:52.300
the statesman who has served three reigns.

42:54.230 --> 42:55.230
You want to leave,

42:55.800 --> 42:56.710
but can you?

42:57.560 --> 42:58.590
We're all just pawns

42:58.590 --> 43:00.800
in the hands of these old men.
